    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken breast portions </strong>to a plate with the<strong> cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Refrigerate until later</p>",
