    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic</strong> <strong>mayo</strong></p>",
