    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>spiced chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Add a couple of splashes of <strong>water</strong> to the pan and cover with a lid</p><p>Cook for a further 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
